title: 820-00165-02 dead
message:
Two pulses is the worst scenario.
I revived one board after heating PCH/CPU with quality flux; accumullated crap underneath can be a cause.

Be sure all volatges from page 11 are present.
Check all SPI Bus Series Termination resistors and their traces.
Also check the LPC bus resistors.
